---
// Urgency.astro - countdown / fear section before checkout
---

<section class="urgency-section">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <div class="urgency-card">
      <div class="fire-emoji" aria-hidden="true">🔥🔥🔥</div>
      <h2>Setiap Detik yang Kamu Tunda, <br/><span class="text-red">Kompetitor Sudah Upload 10 Video Lebih!</span></h2>
      <p class="urgency-desc">
        Bayangkan: Saat kamu masih bimbang, puluhan affiliator lain sudah menjalankan software ini 
        dan <strong>menyedot komisi dari produk yang sama</strong> dengan yang kamu jual. 
        Mereka upload ke 20+ akun sekaligus. Kamu? Masih manual. <strong>Masih satu per satu.</strong>
      </p>
      <div class="fear-stats" aria-label="Statistik kemampuan software">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">20x</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Lebih Cepat Upload</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">50+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Akun Sekaligus</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">24/7</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Non-Stop Otomatis</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="warning-box" role="alert" aria-live="polite">
        ⚠️ <strong>Harga promo ini TIDAK akan bertahan lama.</strong> Begitu kuota habis, harga kembali ke harga normal TANPA DISKON.
      </div>
      <a href="https://prodig.deskomvis.com/checkout-tiktok-autopost" class="btn btn-danger btn-pulse-red" aria-label="Amankan harga promo software sebelum masa diskon berakhir">
        🛒 AMANKAN SEKARANG SEBELUM HARGA NAIK!
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .urgency-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fff 100%);
  }

  .urgency-card {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 50px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.15);
    border: 2px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
  }

  .fire-emoji {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .text-red {
    color: #dc2626;
  }

  .urgency-desc {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    max-width: 650px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .fear-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #dc2626;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .warning-box {
    background: #fef3c7;
    border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #92400e;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    animation: shake 5s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes shake {
    0%, 90%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
    92% { transform: translateX(-4px); }
    94% { transform: translateX(4px); }
    96% { transform: translateX(-4px); }
    98% { transform: translateX(4px); }
  }

  .btn-danger {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 18px 40px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 50px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.5);
  }

  .btn-danger:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 30px -5px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.6);
  }

  .btn-pulse-red {
    animation: pulseRed 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulseRed {
    0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.7); }
    70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 15px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0); }
    100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(220, 38, 38, 0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .urgency-card { padding: 40px 20px; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .fear-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
    .btn-danger { width: 100%; justify-content: center; font-size: 1rem; padding: 16px 24px; }
  }
</style>
